---
title: Hidden Veggie Beef Bolognese Note: Blender required
description: Bust out your blender or food processor and load up your beef Bolognese with a big dose of “hidden” veggies! You’ll boost your sauce by blending in carrots and zucchini, where they can’t be seen (but can be devoured!). Swirl with créme fraîche for an extra-rich texture, then toss with tender rigatoni and Parmesan for a bowl that can’t be beat.
